We performed tiled observations of LIGO/VIRGO event S190421ar (GCN #24141)
with the TAROT-Reunion (Les Makes Observatory, La RÃ©union Island, France)
telescope operating in clear filter.

The observation started on 04/22/19 17:19:22 UTC which corresponds
approximately to 19.7 hours after the GW trigger time.

